# Project Structure

## Overview
- The project is a React application built with TypeScript, Vite, and TailwindCSS
- The entry point is [src/main.tsx](mdc:src/main.tsx)
- Styles are defined in [src/globals.css](mdc:src/globals.css)

## Directory Structure
- [src/features/](mdc:src/features) - Contains feature-specific modules
- [src/page/](mdc:src/page) - Contains page components
- [src/utils/](mdc:src/utils) - Contains utility functions and components
- [src/scripts/](mdc:src/scripts) - Contains build scripts and tools

## Key Features
- [src/features/editor/](mdc:src/features/editor) - Markdown editor based on CodeMirror v6
- [src/features/system/](mdc:src/features/system) - System-level functionality
- [src/features/command/](mdc:src/features/command) - Command handling
- [src/features/history/](mdc:src/features/history) - Edit history functionality
